---
import Layout from '../layouts/Layout.astro';
---

<Layout title="Privacy Policy | Your Service">
  <section class="bg-[#FAF8F5] text-[#3d1d0e] py-16 md:py-24 px-6 min-h-screen w-full">
    
    <div class="mx-auto max-w-7xl bg-white  p-8 md:p-16 border border-gray-100 shadow-sm">
      
      <header class="border-b border-gray-100 pb-6 mb-10 flex flex-col gap-2">
        <h1 class="text-3xl md:text-5xl font-black tracking-tight text-[#3d1d0e]">
            Privacy <span class="text-brand-blue">Policy</span>
        </h1>
        <p class="text-gray-400 font-medium text-xs md:text-sm">
            Last updated: June 11, 2026 • Effective Date: Immediate
        </p>
      </header>

      <div class="flex flex-col gap-12 text-gray-600 font-medium text-base leading-relaxed space-y-">
        
        <div class="flex flex-col gap-3">
          <h2 class="text-xl md:text-2xl font-extrabold text-[#3d1d0e] tracking-tight">
            1. Introduction
          </h2>
          <p>
            Welcome to <strong class="text-[#3d1d0e]">Your Service</strong>. We value your privacy and are deeply committed to protecting your personal data. This Privacy Policy outlines how we collect, use, disclose, and safeguard your information when you visit our website or utilize our outsourcing and virtual assistant services.
          </p>
        </div>

        <div class="flex flex-col gap-3">
          <h2 class="text-xl md:text-2xl font-extrabold text-[#3d1d0e] tracking-tight">
            2. Information We Collect
          </h2>
          <p>We may collect information about you in a variety of ways, primarily classified into:</p>
          <ul class="list-disc list-outside ml-6 flex flex-col gap-2 text-sm md:text-base">
            <li>
              <strong class="text-[#3d1d0e]">Personal Data:</strong> Names, email addresses, phone numbers, corporate details, and billing infrastructure information provided voluntarily when contacting us or hiring our services.
            </li>
            <li>
              <strong class="text-[#3d1d0e]">Derivative Data:</strong> Operational logs, IP addresses, browser types, access schedules, and pages viewed directly prior to and immediately following website navigation.
            </li>
          </ul>
        </div>

        <div class="flex flex-col gap-3">
          <h2 class="text-xl md:text-2xl font-extrabold text-[#3d1d0e] tracking-tight">
            3. How We Use Your Information
          </h2>
          <p>Having accurate information allows us to provide you with a smooth, efficient, and customized outsourcing experience. Specifically, we use your data to:</p>
          <ul class="list-disc list-outside ml-6 flex flex-col gap-2 text-sm md:text-base">
            <li>Facilitate team matching and organize administrative onboarding procedures.</li>
            <li>Process financial transactions, execute billing cycles, and deliver services.</li>
            <li>Fulfill statutory tax duties, corporate liabilities, or active legal compliance.</li>
            <li>Deliver targeted technical notifications, newsletter updates, and promotional insights.</li>
          </ul>
        </div>

        <div class="flex flex-col gap-3">
          <h2 class="text-xl md:text-2xl font-extrabold text-[#3d1d0e] tracking-tight">
            4. Data Protection & Security
          </h2>
          <p>
            We enforce industry-standard administrative, technical, and physical security parameters to secure sensitive corporate data. While we incorporate enterprise-grade safeguards to protect data transmission, please note that no interactive system can be completely impervious to malicious exploits.
          </p>
          <div class="p-4 bg-brand-blue/5 border-l-4 border-brand-blue rounded-r-xl text-sm font-semibold text-brand-blue mt-2">
            Note: All virtual assistant workstations use standard operational encryption protocols to protect day-to-day data management.
          </div>
        </div>

        <div class="flex flex-col gap-3">
          <h2 class="text-xl md:text-2xl font-extrabold text-[#3d1d0e] tracking-tight">
            5. Cookies & Tracking Technologies
          </h2>
          <p>
            Our website uses cookies, web beacons, and analytical monitoring frameworks to customize consumer journeys and optimize overall layout metrics. You can adjust your native browser settings to reject automated cookie integration, though doing so might disrupt certain features of the platform.
          </p>
        </div>

        <div class="flex flex-col gap-3">
          <h2 class="text-xl md:text-2xl font-extrabold text-[#3d1d0e] tracking-tight">
            6. Your Privacy Rights
          </h2>
          <p>
            Depending on your geographic location, you may hold structural data control rights. This includes requesting transparent summaries of your stored data, requesting data erasure, or revoking consent for marketing distributions at any given time.
          </p>
        </div>

        <div class="flex flex-col gap-3">
          <h2 class="text-xl md:text-2xl font-extrabold text-[#3d1d0e] tracking-tight">
            7. Updates to This Policy
          </h2>
          <p>
            We reserve the active right to modify this Privacy Policy at any time. We will alert you about any revisions by updating the "Last updated" date visible at the top of this documentation block.
          </p>
        </div>

        <div class="flex flex-col gap-3 border-t border-gray-100 pt-8 mt-4">
          <h2 class="text-xl md:text-2xl font-extrabold text-[#3d1d0e] tracking-tight">
            8. Contact Us
          </h2>
          <p>If you have any questions or feedback regarding our privacy protocols, please feel free to reach out to our legal compliance desk:</p>
          
          <div class="bg-[#FAF8F5] p-6 border border-gray-100 flex flex-col gap-2 text-sm font-bold text-[#3d1d0e] max-w-md mt-2">
            <span class="text-gray-400 font-semibold uppercase tracking-wider text-xs">Primary Operations Office</span>
            <span class="flex items-center gap-2">
              <span class="w-2 h-2 rounded-full bg-brand-green"></span>
              Email: info@yourservice.com
            </span>
          </div>
        </div>

      </div>
    </div>
  </section>
</Layout>